flowRoot.flowPara: As individual voters, we have several choices: Clinton, Trump, third parties, or not voting at all. But as a country, we will have one of two people as our next president.
Make the decision you’ll be most comfortable with, but remember that your choice has an impact.
Don’t take your vote for granted.
